    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion, and honestly, she still purrs like a dream every time I turn the key. She\u2019s got a few tiny character marks here and there\u2014just proof of all the great road trips we\u2019ve shared\u2014but she\u2019s been pampered and kept clean where it counts. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s ready to hit the open road today with plenty of soul, you've found it. Come on over, let's talk shop, and I'll get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This chassis is a masterclass in balanced engineering, featuring a high-revving power plant with meticulously optimized valve timing and a linear torque curve. I\u2019ve prioritized drivetrain integrity, recently refreshing the cooling system with a high-flow water pump and reinforced silicone hosing to ensure peak thermal management during spirited sessions. The suspension geometry has been fine-tuned for neutral turn-in, utilizing upgraded bushings to reduce deflection and improve tactile feedback through the rack. Every fluid swap has been performed at abbreviated intervals using high-zinc synthetic lubricants to preserve rod bearing health. This is a driver\u2019s specimen, mechanically dialed and structurally rigid, offering a level of visceral engagement that modern, over-assisted platforms simply cannot replicate.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid runner. Clean title. No issues. Priced to move today. Cash only.",
      "price": 28000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
