    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you carve through coastal switchbacks, the rhythmic hum of a twin-cam engine serenading the evening air. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule of golden-age motoring. Clad in a hue that captures the spirit of the open road, every curve of its hand-sculpted body tells a story of weekend escapes and spirited drives. Inside, the scent of aged leather and the tactile click of vintage switchgear ground you in a more visceral era of driving. It possesses that rare, soulful character that modern machines have long since forgotten\u2014a few marks of a life well-lived only add to its undeniable charm. It\u2019s ready for a new custodian to write the next chapter of its journey.",
      "price": 36500.0,
