    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for stopping by to check out my pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for weekend getaways and morning cruises, and honestly, it still puts a huge smile on my face every time I turn the key. It\u2019s in wonderful shape\u2014sure, it has a couple of tiny 'character marks' from the road, but that just shows it\u2019s been loved and driven exactly how it was meant to be. The engine is as smooth as silk and the interior feels like home. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee and take it for a spin!",
