    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically dialed-in F80 M3. This S55-powered machine features a surgical-grade maintenance history with frequent fluid intervals and Blackstone oil analysis to ensure the twin-scroll turbos are operating at peak efficiency. The 7-speed DCT exhibits zero clutch slippage with lightning-fast shift logic, and the active M-differential provides precise torque vectoring through every apex. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from a recent suspension refresh to maintain factory-spec kinematics. If you\u2019re looking for a turn-key performance icon that hasn't been abused on the track but is fully prepared for it, this is the one.",
